
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html dir="ltr">
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html;charset=UTF-8" />
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="./images/icon/reunion-r.png" type="image/x-icon" media="screen"/>
	<title>{{title}}</title>
<style>
html {font-size:100.01%;}
body {font-size:75%;color:#222;background:#E5E5E5;font-family: Arial;}
#container {position:absolute;top:0;left:50%;margin-left:-400px;width:800px;background:#FFF;}
#container .header {float:left;width:100%;height:60px;line-height:60px;margin-bottom:20px;background:#003A83 url("{{abs_path}}/images/bg/top-bg.png") right;border-bottom:3px solid #D61027;color:#FFFFFF;}
#container .header .logo {float:left;display:block;width:90px;height:33px;margin:13px 20px;background:url('{{abs_path}}/images/bg/reunion-logo-top.png') no-repeat;}
#container .header .title {float:left;width:550px;text-align:center;font-size:28px;}
#container .header .date {float:right;width:100px;height:50px;margin-top:5px;}
#container .header .date .day {float:left;width:100px;height:35px;line-height:35px;font-size:42px;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;}
#container .header .date .year {float:left;width:100px;height:15px;line-height:15px;font-size:12px;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;}
#container .content .line {float:left;width:760px;margin:10px 20px 0 20px;}
#container .content .title {font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;}
#container .content .subtitle {background:#e0eeff;padding:5px 10px;width:740px;}
#container .content .message {}
#container .content .red {color:#D61027;font-weight:bold;margin-left:5px;}

#container .footer {float:left;width:760px;margin:20px 20px;padding:15px 0;border-top:2px solid #007DC9;}
#container .footer .message {}
#container .footer .splitline {}
#container .footer .copyright {margin-top:20px;}


</style>
</head>
<body>
	
	<div id="container">
		<div class="header">
			<div class="logo"></div>
			<div class="title">兰蔻24小时监测报告</div>
			<div class="date">
				<span class="day">09</span>
				<span class="year">2013,10</span>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="content">
			<div class="line title">{{title}}</div>
			<div class="line subtitle">微博<span class="red">Top5</span></div>
			<div class="line msghead">每日大智慧消息20131008 - 股票基金 - 乐彩论坛 - bbs.17500.cn </div>
			<div class="line msgcontetn">每日大智慧消息20131008 - 股票基金 - 乐彩论坛 - bbs.17500.cn </div>
		</div>
		<div class="footer">
			<div class="message">本邮件是根据您在文思海辉ReUnion监测服务中开启了关键词邮件订阅服务，用于提醒您最近24小时之内网络媒体报道情况与微博话题提及情况的监测趋势变更，如需关闭，请登录ReUnion进行设置。 </div>
			<div class="splitline"></div>
			<div class="copyright">&copy;2013 Pactera Group. All Rights Reserved.</div>
		</div>
		
	</div>
	
	
	
	
</body>
</html>